'''Christopher Gill Harman''' is a British insurance broker and underwriter who is a name at [[Lloyd's of London]].<ref>[http://www.lloyds.com/~/media/files/the%20market/communications/corporate%20notices/christopher%20harman%20candidate%20statements%20photos_pg%20nos.pdf Christopher Gill Harman.] Lloyd's. 30 November 2012. Retrieved 25 August 2015.</ref>
Harman is a [[Philately|philatelist]] who was formerly president of the [[Royal Philatelic Society London]].<ref>[http://www.rpsl.org.uk/society_officers.asp Officers, Council, Past Presidents & Staff.] Royal Philatelic Society London. Retrieved 17 August 2015.</ref> He signed the [[Roll of Distinguished Philatelists]] in 2003.
