'''Tang Xiaodan''' ({{zh|s=汤晓丹}}; 22 February 1910 &ndash; 21 January 2012) was a Chinese [[film director]].<ref name="death">{{cite web |url=http://www.9abc.net/index.php/archives/72656 |title=The new Chinese war film Father of the film director Tang Xiaodan death |accessdate=20 February 2012 |work=9abc.net |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120130072926/http://www.9abc.net/index.php/archives/72656 |archivedate=30 January 2012 |df=dmy-all }}</ref> In 1984, he won the [[Golden Rooster Award for Best Director]].

